      "id": "1lgp08a20",
      "questionNumber": 1,
      "questionText": "<p>The output from NAND gate having inputs A and B given below will be,</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgpkmftn/2d9d82ba-6686-4cbc-95f7-601b6537088d/52dccfa0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkmfto.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgpkmftn/2d9d82ba-6686-4cbc-95f7-601b6537088d/52dccfa0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkmfto.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-height: 50vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 13th April Evening Shift Physics - Semiconductor Question 74 English\"></p>",
      "options": [
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgpkoswv/db7a7629-148e-49af-82a4-11f3980bb054/9497bef0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkosww.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgpkoswv/db7a7629-148e-49af-82a4-11f3980bb054/9497bef0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkosww.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 13th April Evening Shift Physics - Semiconductor Question 74 English Option 1\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgpkp2ez/4b185774-373b-47c0-9412-b9068ba8f926/9bef04b0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkp2f0.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgpkp2ez/4b185774-373b-47c0-9412-b9068ba8f926/9bef04b0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkp2f0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 13th April Evening Shift Physics - Semiconductor Question 74 English Option 2\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgpkpg7c/5c5b4ca3-b2f6-44d0-8a3b-782e44ed596d/a695c390-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkpg7d.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgpkpg7c/5c5b4ca3-b2f6-44d0-8a3b-782e44ed596d/a695c390-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkpg7d.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 13th April Evening Shift Physics - Semiconductor Question 74 English Option 3\">",
        "<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgpkpq9r/722e3d63-8b22-48a8-b357-55668a827f7a/ae5c6cf0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkpq9s.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgpkpq9r/722e3d63-8b22-48a8-b357-55668a827f7a/ae5c6cf0-dfb9-11ed-ae63-1b5c56cec3c4/file-1lgpkpq9s.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 13th April Evening Shift Physics - Semiconductor Question 74 English Option 4\">"
      ],
      "correctOption": 1,
