      "difficulty": "Easy",
      "solution": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n&\\text {Truth table for NAND gate is }\\\\\\\\\n&\\begin{array}{|c|c|c|}\n\\hline \\mathrm{A} & \\mathrm{B} & \\mathrm{Y}=\\overline{\\mathrm{A} \\cdot \\mathrm{B}} \\\\\n\\hline 0 & 0 & 1 \\\\\n\\hline 0 & 1 & 1 \\\\\n\\hline 1 & 0 & 1 \\\\\n\\hline 1 & 1 & 0 \\\\\n\\hline\n\\end{array}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$<br/><br/>\nOn the basis of given input $\\mathrm{A}$ and $\\mathrm{B}$ the truth table is<br/><br/>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;width:100%}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\">\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">$\\mathrm{A}$</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">$\\mathrm{B}$</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">$\\mathrm{Y}$</th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
      "section": "A",
